rows.label: tlk43300046_05_msg0001
rows.name:
According to rumor, Queen Lagert
ate the Fire Dragons' cooking
at the summit in Acedia...

rows.label: tlk43300046_05_msg0002
rows.name:
What's worse, she supposedly
called it "very fine"...

rows.label: tlk43300046_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Man, I wonder what kind of meal the
Fire Dragons could have made... What
I wouldn't give to try it...

rows.label: tlk43300046_05_msg0004
rows.name:
After all, I need to know what I'm
up against before I can come up
with a dish to outshine them all!
